'''司亞樂'''（{{lang-en|'''Sierra Wireless'''}}），是一家[[無線通訊|無線通訊]]設備公司，總部位於加拿大不列顛哥倫比亞省[[列治文市|列治文市]]。其主要產品爲[[物聯網|物聯網]]與[[機器對機器|M2M]]通訊用途的[[行動通訊|行動通訊]][[模組|模組]]、[[网关|閘道器]]及[[路由器|路由器]]；其被應用在諸多領域，諸如交通運輸、能源、醫療、保全、電腦網路通訊、行動計算、消費性電子等等。業務範圍遍佈世界各地，目前在美國、法國、中國及中國香港設有分公司。

他們的產品通常直接出貨給[[OEM|OEM]]客户，或者透过代理商與經銷商銷售。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.reuters.com/finance/stocks/companyProfile?symbol=SWIR.O |title=Sierra Wireless Inc (SWIR.O)  Company Profile |website=Reuters |accessdate=2016-09-22 |archive-date=2017-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170112025355/http://www.reuters.com/finance/stocks/companyProfile?symbol=SWIR.O |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/SWIR/profile |title=SWIR Profile |website=Yahoo Finance |accessdate=2016-09-22 |archive-date=2017-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170112021734/https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/SWIR/profile |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://money.cnn.com/quote/profile/profile.html?symb=SWIR |title=SWIR - Sierra Wireless Inc Company Profile |website=CNNMoney |accessdate=2016-09-22 |archive-date=2017-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170112022405/http://money.cnn.com/quote/profile/profile.html?symb=SWIR |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 沿革 ==
1993年，由於認爲[[蜂窩數位封包數據|蜂窩數位封包數據]]產業大有可爲，諾曼·湯姆斯（Norman Toms）與安德魯·哈里斯（Andrew Harries）在{{link-en|PMC-Sierra|PMC-Sierra}}公司的支持之下，於5月31日在加拿大溫哥華成立司亞樂公司。他們在創業初期即遇上[[網際網路泡沫|網際網路泡沫]]，目睹一些較早進入這個市場的同行陸續倒閉、破產。撐過數年的辛苦經營，司亞樂逐漸成爲無線通訊軟硬體市場的要角。1999年，於[[多伦多证券交易所|加拿大]]上市；隨後，2000年於美國[[納斯達克|納斯達克]]上市。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/technology/sierra-wireless-founder-norman-toms/article20461566/ |title=Sierra Wireless founder Norman Toms |website=The Globe and Mail |author=Ian Johnson |date=200-04-25 |accessdate=2016-09-22 |archive-date=2016-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161002092746/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/technology/sierra-wireless-founder-norman-toms/article20461566/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>上市後擁有充裕的資金，司亞樂開始積極併購以擴張其產品線及市場佔有率。2003年，它以370萬美元的股份併購了高速CDMA通訊模組廠商中的翹楚AirPrime，該產品線至今仍爲司亞樂的主力。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rcrwireless.com/article/20030617/sub/sierra-wireless-shares-up-on-airprime-acquisition  |title=Sierra Wireless shares up on AirPrime acquisition |author=Reily Gregson |website=RCR Wireless |date=2003-06-17 |accessdate=2016-09-22}}</ref> 

2007年3月6日，司亞樂公告它以2700萬美元的現金及股票併購了設於加州、提供高端行動通訊設備的公司AirLink。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/03/06/idUSIN20070306163450SWIR20070306 |title=Sierra Wireless announces acquisition of AirLink Communications |website=Reuters |date=2007-03-06 |accessdate=2016-09-22 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924090626/http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/03/06/idUSIN20070306163450SWIR20070306 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>2008年8月，併購位於西雅圖的Junxion，金額並未揭露。這是一家以[[Linux|Linux]]爲基礎開發[[無線接取器|行動通訊接取器]]及[[路由器|路由器]]的公司。<ref>{{cite press release|title=Sierra Wireless Completes Asset Purchase Agreement with Junxion, Inc.|publisher=Sierra Wireless|date=August 5, 2008|url=http://www.sierrawireless.com/en/Newsroom/newsreleases/2008/08-05-sierra_wireless_completes_asset_purchase_agreement_with_junxion.aspx|accessdate=March 27, 2013|archive-date=2012-10-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121014085846/http://www.sierrawireless.com/en/Newsroom/newsreleases/2008/08-05-sierra_wireless_completes_asset_purchase_agreement_with_junxion.aspx|dead-url=yes}}</ref>
 
2008年12月，司亞樂向{{link-en|Wavecom|Wavecom}}——一家法國M2M無線通訊公司——提出現金善意收購，這筆交易最終以2.75億萬美元成交。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/1085763/000119312508247262/dex99a29.htm|title=Transcript of Conference Call Held on Dec 2, 2008 at 8:00 A.M. (EST)|accessdate=2016-09-22|archive-date=2013-05-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130528225703/http://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/1085763/000119312508247262/dex99a29.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>2012年8月，以現金4.49千萬歐元收購了{{link-en|蕯基姆通訊|SAGEMCOM}}的M2M業務，並承擔其債務。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.reuters.com/finance/stocks/SWIR.O/key-developments/article/2582900|title=Sierra Wireless, Inc. Completes Acquisition Of Sagemcom M2M Business|accessdate=2016-09-22|archive-date=2014-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140106041845/http://www.reuters.com/finance/stocks/SWIR.O/key-developments/article/2582900|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2012年11月，司亞樂已被科技行業研究公司ABI Research認爲是M2M通訊模組市場的領先者，其佔有率達34%。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.slideshare.net/sierrawireless/sierra-wireless-corporateoverviewnovember2012|title=Sierra Wireless Corporate Overview|accessdate=November 29, 2012|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130126103806/http://www.slideshare.net/sierrawireless/sierra-wireless-corporateoverviewnovember2012|archivedate=2013年1月26日}}</ref>

不過，該公司也有切割業務的時候。2013年1月，爲了集中資源衝刺M2M業務，它將屬於消費性產品的AirCard業務以1.38億美元現金搭配近650萬美元債務賣給[[网件|美國網件公司]]，近160名的相關員工都一併轉移<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/ericsavitz/2013/01/28/sierra-wireless-to-sell-aircard-unit-to-netgear-for-144-5-million/ |title=Sierra Wireless To Sell AirCard Unit To Netgear For $144.5M |author=Eric Savitz |website=Forbes |date=2013-01-28 |accessdate=2016-09-22 |archive-date=2017-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170112002734/http://www.forbes.com/sites/ericsavitz/2013/01/28/sierra-wireless-to-sell-aircard-unit-to-netgear-for-144-5-million/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。稍後，同年10月，宣佈以590萬美元將AnyDATA公司的內嵌式M2M模組及[[數據機|數據機]]業務併入旗下<ref>{{cite web|author1=Andrew Berg|title=Sierra Wireless Acquires AnyData Corp.|url=https://www.wirelessweek.com/news/2013/10/sierra-wireless-acquires-anydata-corp|website=WirelessWeek|accessdate=2016-09-22|date=2013-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170112000959/https://www.wirelessweek.com/news/2013/10/sierra-wireless-acquires-anydata-corp|archive-date=2017-01-12|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

2015年，該公司又大動作地收購了3家公司：1月，完成對瑞典M2M通訊與[[雲端運算|雲端服務]]公司Wireless Maingate的收購<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.proactiveinvestors.com/companies/news/104809/sierra-wireless-buys-swedens-wireless-maingate-in-bid-to-expand-m2m-connectivity-services-58961.html |title=Sierra Wireless buys Sweden's Wireless Maingate in bid to expand M2M connectivity services |author=Deborah Bacal |website=Proactive Investors North America |date=2014-12-22 |accessdate=2016-09-22 |archive-date=2017-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170112012041/http://www.proactiveinvestors.com/companies/news/104809/sierra-wireless-buys-swedens-wireless-maingate-in-bid-to-expand-m2m-connectivity-services-58961.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>；5月，宣布收購北美[[移動寬頻|移動寬頻]]技術與服務的佼佼者Accel Networks<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.wirelessweek.com/news/2015/05/sierra-wireless-acquires-accel-networks |title=Sierra Wireless Acquires Accel Networkss |author=Andrew Berg |website=WirelessWeek |date=2015-05-07 |accessdate=2016-09-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170112001003/https://www.wirelessweek.com/news/2015/05/sierra-wireless-acquires-accel-networks |archive-date=2017-01-12 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>；6月，宣佈收購專注於M2M及[[車載資訊系統|車載資訊系統]]市場的法國[[行動虛擬營運商|行動虛擬營運商]]MobiquiThings。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rudebaguette.com/2015/06/24/sierra-wireless-acquire-mobiquithings-scale-iot-network/ |title=Sierra Wireless acquire Mobiquithings to scale up their IoT Network |author=Liam Boogar |website=Rude Baguette |date=2015-06-24 |accessdate=2016-09-22 |archive-date=2017-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170112000847/http://www.rudebaguette.com/2015/06/24/sierra-wireless-acquire-mobiquithings-scale-iot-network/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

根據ABI Research針對2015年度M2M通訊模組市場的調查報告顯示，司亞樂已連續5年位居該市場營業額首位，超出第二位達1.75億美元。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.abiresearch.com/press/new-market-dynamic-brewing-sierra-wireless-leads-m/ |title=New Market Dynamic Brewing as Sierra Wireless Leads M2M Module Revenues but SIMCom Wireless Leads in Shipments |author= |website=ABI Research |date=2016-06-20 |accessdate=2016-09-22 |archive-date=2017-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170112003512/https://www.abiresearch.com/press/new-market-dynamic-brewing-sierra-wireless-leads-m/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

